{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7a0c1fd2ef","title":"应先打小仗然后才有可能打较大的仗","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ba3df9e260","index":0,"year":1950,"month":7,"day":26,"articleId":"7a0c1fd2ef"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"bb17242181","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"7a0c1fd2ef","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东为中央人民政府人民革命军事委员会起草的给中国人民解放军西南军区副司令员、云南军区司令员陈的电报。陈康当时奉派越南，以中共中央代表身份协助越共中央和越南人民军总部组织指挥抗击法国侵略军的边界战役。"},{"id":"b85933c1c9","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"7a0c1fd2ef","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指陈质1950年7月22日13时给中共中央驻越共中央联络代表罗贵波并报中共中央、中共中央西南局等的电报。"}],"contents":[{"id":"8eeaf4caee","type":"title","text":"应先打小位然后才有可能打较大的仗”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"7a0c1fd2ef"},{"id":"bb17242181","type":"paragraph","text":"陈赛：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"7a0c1fd2ef"},{"id":"b85933c1c9","type":"paragraph","text":"七月二十二日十三时电悉。我们认为你的意见是正确的。越军应先打小仗，逐步锻炼能打稍为大一点的仗，然后才可能打较大的仗。目前不要直打高平，先打小据点，并争取围城打援是适当的。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"7a0c1fd2ef"},{"id":"a1876b6f1b","type":"subtitle","text":"军委","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"7a0c1fd2ef"},{"id":"21d9292b45","type":"paragraph","text":"七月二十六日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"7a0c1fd2ef"}],"page":{"id":"5cc2e24595","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"7a0c1fd2ef","start":49,"end":49}}}},"__N_SSG":true}